            "title": "美国就业市场承压：八月裁员率显著高于疫情前水平",
            "description": "<div><figure class=\"image\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://img.jin10.com/news/25/09/LOONnD9quJyH4bUmqSRVW.jpg\" title=\"\"/></figure></div>",
            "image": "https://img.jin10.com/news/25/09/00zoujHYHWjTOukha76FO.png/lite",
            "link": "https://xnews.jin10.com/details/190449",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-05 17:19:53",
